    dc:creator "Silva, Fabio Laurindo Da; Oliveira, Caroline Silva Neubern De" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Tanypus urszulae, a new Tanypodinae (Diptera: Chironomidae) from the Neotropical Region" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.163680>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.163681>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.163682> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.163680>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Tanypus urszulae Silva sp. nov., adult male. (1) Terminal flagellomere. (2) Wing. (3) Fore tibial spur. (4) Mid tibial spurs. (5) Hind tibial spurs. (6) Abdomen, dorsal view, showing coloration pattern. (7) Hypopygium, left: ventral aspect, right: dorsal aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/163680/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.163681>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 11. Tanypus urszulae Silva sp. nov., pupa. (8) Frontal apotome. (9) Thoracic horn. (10) Abdomen with chaetotaxy, dorsal view. (11) Anal lobe and male genital sac, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/163681/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.163682>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 19. Tanypus urszulae Silva sp. nov., larva. (12) Head with chaetotaxy, left: ventral aspect, right: dorsal aspect. (13) Antenna. (14) Apex of antenna. (15) Basal segment of maxillary palp. (16) Mandible. (17) Mentum and M appendage. (18) Ligula and paraligulae. (19) Claws of posterior parapod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/163682/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

